  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And there was another fellow who was an interpreter who had a German title of nobility who was half Jewish named von [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were a couple more there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I-- at the court house, I'm not even sure how I got my orders.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It may have been that I went in to see Telford Taylor who was the chief prosecutor at this point, but I was assigned immediately to read all the transcripts of all the cases that had been decided to date and prepare a manual for the use of the prosecution on evidentiary rulings.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was quite educational, got me into the transcript of the main Nuremberg trial and also the ongoing proceedings which were under way then, the justice case, the doctor's case.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were a great variety of cases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it also got me into documentation for these cases, which I found horrifying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, these were German accounts of German conduct and they were totally horrifying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I would read this stuff and get drenched in it all day long, meanwhile plucking out a few evidentiary rulings as I went along, but I got absorbed in the substance as well.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the documentation, as far as I was concerned, was more horrible than any of the fiction I've ever read or seen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this went on for months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just kept on reading the stuff and reading the stuff.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So during the day, generally, my reaction was one of enormous disgust and contempt and a lot of adrenaline shooting into my blood streams, and then I would walk out on the street in the middle of this German population, not knowing who I was ever dealing with, you know?",
      "word_count": 50
    }
  ],
